ygData.msgSnippet: Is the faction called Clerics of Tunare ? If so, go to wFP buy a lot of muffins from a baker and give them to a dwarf in the same zone. For more details,
ygData.messageBody:
Is the faction called "Clerics of Tunare"? If so, go to wFP buy a lot of
muffins from a baker and give them to a dwarf in the same zone. For more
details, Hevan, contact me in-game. 6copper per muffin. 16 faction increases
for 16 muffins you give.


Mazy
Prexus
